Map

Use em_map to add the map, simply pass the name of the country, a valid name as returned by em_bank, then reference that name in e_map.

library(echarts4r)
library(echarts4r.maps)

USArrests$state <- row.names(USArrests) # add states as column

USArrests %>% 
  e_charts(state) %>%
  em_map("USA") %>% 
  e_map(Murder, map = "USA") %>% 
  e_visual_map(Murder)
